name: ConvertCelsiustoFahrenheit
0:
”Alexa, open Celsius Fahrenheit”
”Alexa, open Celsius Fahrenheit and convert 10 Celsius”
”Alexa, open Celsius Fahrenheit and 10 Celsius”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: celsius fahrenheit
des:
This skill converts a Celsius value to its corresponding Fahrenheit value.
When prompted for the Celsius say the Celsius value. This can be any positive number.
The skill will respond with the corresponding Fahrenheit value.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
